channel.description:
Welcome to the Let's Play community channel! A community hub filled with content created and submitted by the community featuring the Let's Play crew: Achievement Hunter, Funhaus, ScrewAttack, Kinda Funny, The Creatures and Cow Chop. Interested in getting more involved with the community? Consider checking out the content here, or even better, make your own content!

Who can submit?
Anyone, especially you.

What can I submit?
Anything that fits into a video format. Some examples include animations, compilations, speed art, music remixes, and how to videos.

How do I submit videos?
Check out our group page to see the details on how to get your content to us: http://roosterteeth.com/group/lets-play-community

channel.description:
Rocket Beans TV steht für 24/7-Entertainment-Power rund um Gaming und Popkultur!
Seit seinem Start am 15.01.2015 hat sich Deutschlands einziger unabhängiger Online-TV-Sender zum europaweit erfolgreichsten Kanal auf der Streaming-Plattform Twitch entwickelt. Mit seinem interaktiven, ungewöhnlichen Programmangebot und Auftritten prominenter Gäste (z.B. Moritz Bleibtreu, André Schürrle, Smudo uvm.), begeistern die Rocket Beans bis zu 120.000 Zuschauer täglich. Ausgezeichnet mit dem Deutschen Webvideopreis 2014 und 2015 sowie dem 1. Deutschen Content Marketing Preis desselben Jahres gestaltet Rocket Beans TV die Fernsehunterhaltung der Zukunft.

I owe everything to my viewers from all around the world. Your support and willingness to learn guitar keeps me moving forward towards my mission to teach guitar! 

You can Subscribe to this channel for regular uploads and make sure you follow me on my Facebook and Instagram page for more great stuff! 

I look forward to help you progress in your journey. I wish you all the success. 

Thank you
Keep playing!

channel.description:
We're here to play some games, and help you relax. We are an ASMR channel focusing on playing the games that give you brain tingles. Feel free to request certain games or videos in the comments! ASMR is great for relaxation, meditation, relief from anxiety, and a natural sleep aid!

==========================================
SUPPORT LPQ!
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
►https://www.g2a.com/r/letsplayquietly
►IndieBox: http://theindiebox.com?afmc=66

==========================================

What is ASMR?
Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response (ASMR) is a euphoric experience characterized by a static-like tingling sensation on the skin that typically begins on the scalp and moves down the back of the neck and upper spine, precipitating relaxation.

channel.description:
Welcome to the Let's Play With Brigands channel!

I'm Paul (Tony to my friends) and I grew up on many of the games I play on this channel. I'm not the flashiest, whiniest, or (add adjective here)-ist Let's Play guy out there, but I do earnest play throughs and add a bit of comedic observations here or there. People seem to dig what I've done so far so thanks to everyone who has subscribed, commented, or just watched anything I've done.

I upload a new Let's Play every Monday with occasional BONUS let's plays (like a Friday series), so please subscribe to get up with my latest videos.

Check me out on Patreon to access the Let's Play With Brigands Live Archives! - https://www.patreon.com/LetsPlayWithBrigands

I'm also 1/3 of the band "Brigands" (hence the channel name) and I'll generally be throwing in a clip from one of our songs at the end of every "Let's Play", so check out our stuff at http://brigands.bandcamp.com/ for free music downloads or check out http://www.brigandsrock.com.
